cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use TradingAgents-Pro in your research, please cite both this fork and the original paper."
title: "TradingAgents-Pro: Verified Multi-Agent Trading Framework"
abstract: >-
  TradingAgents-Pro extends the TradingAgents multi-agent LLM trading framework
  with a runtime verification layer (per-claim fact-checking, source reliability
  scoring, bias detection, contradiction detection, and forward predictions
  with invalidation criteria). The verification layer is routed through the
  VeroQ API. Built on TradingAgents (Apache-2.0) by Tauric Research.
type: software
authors:
  - name: "Veroq AI"
    website: "https://veroq.ai"
license: "Apache-2.0"
repository-code: "https://github.com/Veroq-ai/TradingAgents-Pro"
url: "https://veroq.ai"
version: "0.1.0"
date-released: "2026-04-23"
keywords:
  - multi-agent
  - llm
  - trading
  - verification
  - fact-checking
  - algorithmic-trading
  - financial-intelligence
references:
